    {\displaystyle {\hat {\sigma }}={\underline {5}}\,1\,3\,{\underline {6}}\,{\underline {8}}\,2\,7\,{\underline {9}}\,4}
  , which allows the reconstruction of the cycles of 
  
    
      
        σ
      
    
    {\displaystyle \sigma }
  .
The following table shows 
  
    
      
        
          
            
              σ
              ^
            
          
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle {\hat {\sigma }}}
   and 
  
    
      
        σ
      
    
